## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **fertility heterogeneity** — female / male / unexplained / age-related each different mechanism. quantum-VQE 의 mechanism-specific design 가능.
2. **IVF success rate** = ~30-50% per cycle (age-dependent), 단 30%+ failure unexplained. quantum 의 hormone receptor optimization 가능성.
3. **germline gene therapy ethics** = CRISPR He Jiankui 2018 case, currently illegal globally. quantum 의 germline-tropic delivery 는 ethical-out-of-scope.
4. **pregnancy complications maternal mortality** — global burden, quantum-design 외부 issue 큰.
5. **contraception research stagnation** = decades-old products (pill / IUD / barrier). quantum-VQE 의 새 mechanism 가능 (sperm-specific).
6. **fertility access economics** — IVF $15-30k per cycle, insurance coverage variable. quantum 외부.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, reproductive 임상 의미 한정.

